data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! ($3,000 Seller Credit now being offered)What an incredible find! This move-in ready, well-maintained 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home with an additional flex/office/nursery space comes with instant peace of mind. The home has several updates that will provide its new owners with the comfort of knowing the major systems have lots of life left (New Roof 2022, New HVAC 2021, New septic lines 2018, New LVP Flooring 2020). The tranquility of the quaint subdivision, ending in a cul-de-sac, allows for privacy and safety. The home's backyard space offers a covered patio and plenty of yard for entertaining or play. The outdoor space is partially shaded and fully fenced (chain link fence New in 2020), which offers safety for those furry family members as well. The attached 1 car garage and the detached storage shed (to convey with purchase) provide plenty of storage. The home's location offers easy access to nearby employment, restaurants, and shopping, as well as close proximity to eastern NC's various military bases (Camp Geiger and New River Air Station approx. 14miles, Camp Lejeune approx. 18miles, and  Stone Bay Range approx. 24miles.). Come see for yourself - schedule your showing today!
